@TomSweeneyRedHat okay figured it out.  https://docs.codecov.io/docs/about-the-codecov-bash-uploader#section-upload-token

So for Travis there's nothing to do, it should "just work".  For Cirrus-CI (after my PR merges) we'll need to follow the instructions to set the env. var to your token, then run the magic bash script.  I can help set this up when we get there.  Otherwise if I'm not around and you want to try, docs are here:

https://cirrus-ci.org/guide/writing-tasks/#encrypted-variables
